Package com.burstly.lib.network.request

Package contains AsyncTask used in project.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAbortableRequest Abstraction on abortable request.
IRequestCallback<T> Implement this interface if you whant to execute some callback.
 

Class Summary
AbortableAsyncTask<T> This class is a parent of all tasks.
CurrencyRequestTask<T> This request task is used to make Currency management related requests.
DefaultRequestCallback<T> Empty implementation for convinience.
DefaultRequestCallbackWrapper<T> This is a default implementation of IRequestCallback wrapper.
ImageFetchTask This task is used to fetch banner image.
RequestManager This class is responsible for making requests to burslty server.
RequestManager.ConnectionInfo Class decribes current connection type.
RequestManager.RequestDataObject<T> Request TO.
SafeAsyncTask<T> AsyncTask wrapper.
SingleHostRequest<T> Request to a single host.
 

Package com.burstly.lib.network.request Description

Package contains AsyncTask used in project. Main request task BurstlyRequestTask to server is placed here.
